LCNG is a LCARS-NG theme for Drupal 6 by G. Nguyen. It's originally based on the sub-theme GENESIS. This theme was inspired by the LCARS-GUI from Star Trek: The Next Generation (TNG)

LCARS-NG is an acronym for "LIBRARY COMPUTER ACCESS/RETRIEVAL SYSTEM â€“ NEXT GENERATION"

FEATURES
- CSS3 rounded-corners with CSS3PIE for optimal curves on Firefox, Chrome and Internet Exlorer.
- fluid layouts
- dynamically fullwindow bars and L-bows with auto height if content fits window height
- different layouts for optimal content display
- context layouts
- support drupal menusystem in sidebar-menus
- user profile page
- user login page

INSTALL
- Just download the project archive and extract all files in the Drupal theme folder "/sites/all/themes/LCNG".

HELP
The frontpage of this theme is a user login page to access LCARS-NG by design. You can add a link to a custom frontpage for public users in the template file "page-front-anonymous.tpl.php".

